  "rationale": "<p>The correct answer is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"94\"><mn>94</mn></math>. Taking the square root of each side of the given equation yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x minus 47 equals 1\"><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>47</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math> or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x minus 47 equals negative 1\"><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>47</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math>. Adding <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"47\"><mn>47</mn></math> to both sides of the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x minus 47 equals 1\"><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>47</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math> yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x equals 48\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>48</mn></math>. Adding <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"47\"><mn>47</mn></math> to both sides of the equation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x minus 47 equals negative 1\"><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>47</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math> yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x equals 46\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>46</mn></math>. Therefore, the sum of the solutions to the given equation is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"48 plus 46\"><mn>48</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>46</mn></math>, or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"94\"><mn>94</mn></math>.</p>",
